name.baseName: Polyvinyl chloride, from emulsion process, E-PVC

dataSetInformation.common:generalComment: Disclaimer: The LCI and LCIA results of this dataset can vary from the published Eco-profile on PlasticsEurope website due to the conversion of the original LCI to an ILCD compliant LCI, and some updates of characterization factors used in the Eco-profile since the time of the publication. This was done in agreement with PlasticsEurope.

time.common:timeRepresentativenessDescription: time to which data mainly refer: 2013

technology.technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesse: The dataset represents the production mix of commercial E-PVC production technologies in Europe

dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativenes.annualSupplyOrProductionVolume: referring to covered E-PVC nameplate capacity (83 % of 791 kt in 2013)
dataSourcesTreatmentAndRepresentativenes.samplingProcedure: Questionnaires sent out to all production units in Europe operated by ECVM member companies.
